Package com.github.cyberryan1.cybercore.spigot.command.helpers

Class SentCommand

java.lang.Object
com.github.cyberryan1.cybercore.spigot.command.helpers.SentCommand
public class SentCommand
extends java.lang.Object
Used to represent an executed command, with the sender and arguments of the command. Allows for one to easily get the arguments of the executed command into a specified type.
Author:
CyberRyan1
